        "section_badr6p": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>California Residents</strong>",
            "text": "<p></p><p>Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) and the California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA), California residents are entitled to specific rights regarding their personal information. These include:</p><p>Right to Know: Request details about the categories and specific pieces of personal information we collect, use, disclose, and sell.</p><p>Right to Delete: Request deletion of your personal information, subject to legal exceptions.</p><p>Right to Opt-Out: Decline the sale or sharing of your personal information.</p><p>Right to Correct: Request corrections of inaccurate personal information.</p><p>Right to Limit Use: Limit the use of sensitive personal information for non-essential purposes.</p><p>To exercise any of these rights, please submit a request via our <a href=\"https://catchco.com/data-subject-access-request\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Data Request Form</span></a>. We will verify your identity and respond to your request in accordance with applicable laws.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "note": ""
          }
        },
        "section_CEaY7t": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>Virginia, Colorado, Connecticut, and Utah Residents</strong>",
            "text": "<p></p><p>Residents of Virginia, Colorado, Connecticut, and Utah have privacy rights under their respective state privacy laws. These rights include:</p><p>Access and Portability: Request access to your personal information and obtain it in a portable and readily usable format.</p><p>Correction: Request updates or corrections to inaccurate personal information.</p><p>Deletion: Request the deletion of your personal information, subject to exceptions.</p><p>Opt-Out: Decline the processing of your personal information for:</p><p>Targeted advertising</p><p>Sale of personal data</p><p>Profiling in furtherance of decisions that produce legal or similarly significant effects</p><p>To exercise these rights, submit a request via our <a href=\"https://catchco.com/data-subject-access-request\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Data Request Form</span></a> or email us at support@mysterytacklebox.com. We will verify your identity as required by law before processing your request.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "note": ""
          }
        },
        "section_exaeMn": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>Non-Discrimination</strong>",
            "text": "<p></p><p>We will not discriminate against you for exercising any of your privacy rights.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "note": ""
          }
        },
        "section_dE4Xiw": {
          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>How to Exercise Your Rights</strong>",
            "text": "<p>To exercise any of the rights described above, you may:</p><p>Fill out our <a href=\"https://catchco.com/data-subject-access-request\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Data Request Form</span></a>.</p><p>Email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\" title=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\">support@mysterytacklebox.com</a></p><p>Please note that we may require additional information to verify your identity before processing your request.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
